Be162B700sub601 algorithm

Source: R/algorithms.R
Be162B700sub601.Rd

Applies the Be162B700sub601 algorithm

Be162B700sub601(w700, w601)

Arguments

w700

numeric. Value at wavelength of 700 nm
w601

numeric. Value at wavelength of 601 nm

Value

RasterLayer or numeric
